{
  "message": "test(polynomial): extend thin metamorphic relations with varied families\n\nAdded 12 fixtures across 6 polynomial metamorphic relations that each\nhad a single case, broadening coefficient shape and poly-family\ncoverage (polynomial1d, chebyshev):\n\n- poly_add_commutative (2): equal-degree polynomial1d with asymmetric\n  coefficient patterns, unequal-degree chebyshev mix\n- poly_mul_commutative (2): chebyshev deg2\u00d7deg2, scalar\u00d7deg3 edge\n- poly_eval_linearity (2): deg4 at negative point with non-unit\n  alpha/beta, zero eval point with unit alpha=beta=1\n- poly_double_derivative_consistent (2): deg5 polynomial1d, deg4\n  chebyshev to exercise the recurrence-based second-derivative path\n- poly_add_associative (2): zero-mixed triangular coefficients,\n  chebyshev unequal-length triplet\n- poly_neg_involution (2): chebyshev geometric-sequence coeffs,\n  all-zero polynomial1d (double-neg must stay zero)\n\n30 polynomial_metamorphic cases total (from 18).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
